OL,3,CCovid nurse shares her experience as
OL,4,Cnew phase of inquiry starts
OL,6,FA nurse who was on the frontline
OL,7,Fduring the pandemic says she and her
OL,8,Fcolleagues are still feeling its
OL,9,Feffects.
OL,11,FAndrea Prince says working in the NHS
OL,12,F"was really difficult" and staff were
OL,13,Fbreaking down in tears with fear.
OL,15,FShe says she hopes lessons will be
OL,16,Flearned from the Covid Inquiry and it
OL,17,Fwill hold decision-makers accountable.
