OL,3,CCovid nurse shares her experience as
OL,4,Cnew phase of inquiry starts
OL,6,FIt comes as other harrowing stories
OL,7,Ffrom patients and NHS workers have
OL,8,Fbeen published by the inquiry
OL,9,Fexamining the impact of coronavirus.
OL,11,FAndrea is a nurse practitioner at the
OL,12,FAneurin Bevan University Health Board.
OL,14,FShe was on the frontline as
OL,15,Fcoronavirus arrived in Wales in 2020.
OL,17,F"I worked the very first shift that
OL,18,FCovid broke and I worked all weekend",
OL,19,Fshe said.
