OL,3,CCovid nurse shares her experience as
OL,4,Cnew phase of inquiry starts
OL,6,F"I don't think anybody felt safe at
OL,7,Fthat time, I think we were all
OL,8,Ffrightened. The biggest fear for me
OL,9,Fwas, not so much for me or my
OL,10,Fpatients, but taking it home to my
OL,11,Ffamily and loved ones."
OL,13,FLeaders from the Health and Safety
OL,14,FExecutive and Unison are expected to
OL,15,Fgive evidence this week as the inquiry
OL,16,Flooks at the governmental and societal
OL,17,Fresponse to Covid-19 by assessing the
OL,18,Fimpact of the pandemic on how NHS
OL,19,Fservices were delivered.
