OL,3,CCovid nurse shares her experience as
OL,4,Cnew phase of inquiry starts
OL,6,F"I think they were unprepared, but
OL,7,Fthen I don't know if anyone could be
OL,8,Fprepared for this."
OL,10,FAndrea wants to see the inquiry hold
OL,11,Fpeople accountable for the decisions
OL,12,Fmade during the pandemic.
OL,14,F"We have to learn lessons, definitely,
OL,15,Ffrom what happened and we have to be
OL,16,Fmore prepared if it ever happens
OL,17,Fagain", she told ITV Cymru Wales.
