OL,3,CCovid nurse shares her experience as
OL,4,Cnew phase of inquiry starts
OL,6,F"I think we need to know the truth,
OL,7,Fand I don't think anything needs to be
OL,8,Fbrushed under the carpet. We need to
OL,9,Fknow if mistakes were made, people
OL,10,Fneed to hold their hands up and say
OL,11,Fsorry."
OL,13,FThe public inquiry examining the
OL,14,Fimpact of the Covid pandemic on NHS
OL,15,Fworkers, patients and the delivery of
OL,16,Fhealthcare began on Monday.
